#: ../../../reference/arrays.ndarray.rst:193
msgid ""
"Array attributes reflect information that is intrinsic to the array itself. "
"Generally, accessing an array through its attributes allows you to get and "
"sometimes set intrinsic properties of the array without creating a new "
"array. The exposed attributes are the core parts of an array and only some "
"of them can be reset meaningfully without creating a new array. Information "
"on each attribute is given below."
